>狄勇</span><p operatercreater="0" /></cell></row><row id="CF2F8F4523" width="660" min-height="400"><cell id="CF2F8F4524" width="660" cell-style="border:;borderSlash:;linear:Solid"><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">向患者或家属或代理人交代术中或术后可能出现的并发症及手术风险： </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0">    </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">1</span><span operatercreater="0">.麻醉意外（详见麻醉知情同意书）；</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">2</span><span operatercreater="0">、术中术后心脑血管意外，多脏器功能衰竭，患者猝死；</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">3</span><span operatercreater="0">、脂肪栓塞，危及生命；</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">4</span><span operatercreater="0">、深静脉血栓及脑栓塞可能；</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">5</span><span operatercreater="0">、术中游离体不能取净，依据具体情况更改手术方式；</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">6</span><span operatercreater="0">、术后症状恢复不满意，骨化性肌炎，关节功能障碍；</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">7</span><span operatercreater="0">、术后切口感染延期愈合或不愈合、切口脂肪液化、缝线反应、切口裂开、血肿脓肿形成；</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">8</span><span operatercreater="0">、术中副损伤：如损伤韧带、肌肉、血管及神经等；</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">9</span><span operatercreater="0">、术后切口感染导致化脓性关节炎可能；</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">10</span><span operatercreater="0">、术后症状缓解不明显，疼痛增加可能；</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">11</span><span operatercreater="0">、加重原有內科疾病；</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0">12</span><span operatercreater="0">、其他一切可能出现的意外及术后并发症。</span><p operatercreater="0" /></cell></row><row id="CF2F990926" width="660"><cell id="CF2F990927" width="660" cell-style="border:;borderSlash:;linear:Solid"><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">患者或代理人意见：</span><p operatercreater="0" />